data.description: Wonderful property located on over 1/3 acre with creek and no flood insurance required! Beautiful yard with stone throughout, outbuilding,Fire Pit,and patio sitting. Large carport with ample storage and RV parking. This home has been designed around spectacular creek. Must see!
